Zhexuan Yang


Installing the scullbuffer device:
--------------------------------------------------
./install.sh

This may need you type the password of root

Testing the functioning of scullbuffer  device:
-------------------------------------------------

To run all test cases:
   sudo test/allTestCases
This will unload/load the module to ensure the tests run cleanly.

To run tests individually:
  sudo ./scull_unload
  sudo ./scull_load
  test/testcase[1-7]

To run the producers and consumers individually:
  ./producer <num_items_to_produce> <color>
  ./consumer <num_items_to_consume>
